Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:35.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}便迎来大家沐浴阳光的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:40.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}亲如一家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:43.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}自然而然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:45.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}永不分离
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:48.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(280,280)\blur3}相守相望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:53.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(280,280)\blur3}采撷点滴温馨 探索奇妙世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:56.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}天空近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:22:01.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}花儿悄然绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:06.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,280)\blur3}静静流淌的日子竟也如此芬芳可爱
